      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-end space-x-2">
        <button
          id="reject-cookies"
          class="font-sora px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Rechazar
        </button>
        <button
